<dl id="n01084d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n01" href="#n01084d">N01 (VI.B.10)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n01all.htm#n01084d"> 84(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> elect. light boxbath</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[BEAUTY&apos;S TORTURE CHAMBER [&hellip;]</font> / By Leonie Duprez] One of London&apos;s most noted beauties has a &ldquo;human repair shop&rdquo; all her own <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> The most extraordinary of all is a machine that irons and dissolves fat <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> When she has stood as much as possible of the ironing business she steps into the <mark>electric light box bath</mark> <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> then she lies on the hard couch while her masseuse pummels her and rubs her with a reducing cream. <small> <a name="DSK23dec22" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#DSK23dec22"><cite title="source">Daily Sketch</cite></a> (23 December 1922) 13/3</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c05146g" href="c05all.htm#c05146g">VI.C.05:146(g)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
